arts.ttl: Go Ahead Eagles earn slender win over Sparta
arts.sum: Go Ahead Eagles defeated Sparta Rotterdam 1-0 in Friday’s Eredivisie action. Gjivai Zechiel made his first start in the midfield for Sparta but his error led to the opening goal. He lost the ball just outside his own box and Jakob Breum punished the youngster.
